title: Paleo Way
description: Through travel and talks with experts, celebrity chef Pete Evans shares information and recipes that showcase the benefits of a paleo lifestyle.

title: Paranormal Survivor
description: In interviews and reenactments, ordinary people relive their terrifying encounters with unwelcome guests from beyond the world of the living.

title: Parrot Heads
description: Dive into the colorful world of Jimmy Buffett's most dedicated fans, who follow the singer from concert to concert and chill out along the way.

title: Patient Seventeen
description: A surgeon claims to remove high tech microchips that aliens used to manipulate the human race. This documentary seeks to separate fact from fiction.

title: Peculiar Pets
description: This offbeat documentary features people with pets that are as unorthodox as they are dangerous, including a crocodile, a lynx and a Komodo dragon.

title: Pentatonix: On My Way Home
description: This concert documentary follows self-proclaimed choir nerds turned Grammy-winning vocal quintet Pentatonix on their sold-out 2015 tour.
actors: Mitch Grassi, Scott Hoying, Avi Kaplan, Kirstie Maldonado

title: Pet Fooled
description: With commentary by two prominent veterinarians, this film looks at the unregulated pet food industry and its negative impact on animals' health.

title: Pet Hoarders
description: Experience the lives of pet owners who open up about their obsessive love of animals and how they care for their massive menageries.

title: Peter and the Farm
description: His hilltop farm in Vermont may be bucolic, but making ends meet is a backbreaking challenge for grizzled, hard-drinking organic farmer Peter Dunning.

title: Prescription Thugs
description: A documentarian uses his own family's experiences as a springboard to explore the ethical issues surrounding the FDA and pharmaceutical industry.

title: Prince Philip: The Plot to Make a King
description: This documentary recounts efforts by England's elite to deny power to royal consort Prince Philip due to his German roots and ambitious family.

title: Print the Legend
description: This award-winning, original documentary chronicles the race for market leadership in 3D printing, the next wave of technological evolution.

title: Prison Women Compilations: Texas Hold 'Em
description: At Dallas County Jail in Texas, women working to guard some of the country's most dangerous inmates are prepared to keep order and command respect.
